Etymology not certain. Probably {{der-lite|zh|sit}}; compare {{cog-lite|bo|аҪ–аҪ„ајӢаҪ–||storeroom; storehouse|sc=Tibt|tr=bang ba}}, {{cog-lite|my|бҖқбҖ„бҖәбҖё||enclosure|sc=Mymr|tr=wang:}} ({{zh-ref|Bodman, 1980}}). Alternatively, compare {{cog-lite|bo|аҪ–аҫІаҪ„||house|sc=Tibt|tr=brang}} (as in {{m-lite|bo|аҪ•аҪјајӢаҪ–аҫІаҪ„||palace|sc=Tibt|tr=pho brang}} and {{m-lite|bo|аҪ–аҫІаҪ„ајӢаҪҒаҪ„||dwelling house|sc=Tibt|tr=brang khang}}) ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

